<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulm</head><p>Der Rat kündigt seine Gesandtschaft zur reichsstädtischen Zusammenkunft wegen Weinsberg an Simon und Judas in Ulm an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_193" id="95v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_193_r1l3">Den von Vlme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_193_r1l4"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> freẅnde ~ <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_193_r1l5"><expan>weinſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_193_r1l6"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnſer <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>fr<ex>ewnden</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_193_r1l7">des <expan>Reıchsſtett<ex>en</ex></expan> . auf ſymonıs et Jude ſchıerıſt gen vlme </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_193_r1l8"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> . von den Jr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan> / es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_193_r1l9"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> denn daʒ vns ſölıch treffenlıch ſache anſtıeſſ . daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_193_r1l10">des auf dıe ʒeıt niht getun <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_193_r1l11"><expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_193_r1l12"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>ıp<ex>ſ</ex>a</expan> dıe <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Luce </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_193" id="95v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Ulme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> frewnde <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Weinsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        unser <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>fr<ex>ewnden</ex></expan> des
                                <expan>reichsstett<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">auf Symonis et Jude schierist</q>28.10.1420</note>
</app> gen Ulme <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, von den ir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan>, es <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> denn, daz
                        uns sölich treffenlich sache anstiess, daz wir des auf die zeit niht getun
                                <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
                        Luce.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
